opportunity /ˌɒpəˈtjuːnɪtɪ/

(opportunities) 

1. N-VAR An opportunity is a situation in which it is possible for you to do something that you want to do. 机会 

例： I had an opportunity to go to New York and study. 我曾有过一个去纽约学习的机会。 

例： ...equal opportunities in employment. …平等的就业机会。

</div>

